<i>"because most letters I get
are from greasy fan boys</i>

1005
01:32:09,280 --> 01:32:11,044
<i>"who think that I'm cute.</i>

1006
01:32:11,120 --> 01:32:14,681
<i>"Keep drawing those comics.
