1011
01:32:40,080 --> 01:32:41,411
<i>and everything looked miniature,</i>

1012
01:32:42,720 --> 01:32:44,370
<i>like the chairs and the monkey bars,</i>

1013
01:32:44,720 --> 01:32:47,200
<i>just much smaller than you remembered?</i>

1014
01:32:50,160 --> 01:32:52,242
<i>I know nothing's changed,</i>

1015
01:32:52,320 --> 01:32:55,005
<i>but everything looks
totally different to me now.</i>

1016
01:33:03,320 --> 01:33:05,049
It's 50 cents.

1017
01:33:05,120 --> 01:33:06,645
Thanks.

1018
01:33:16,120 --> 01:33:17,963
-Hey.
-Hi.

1019
01:33:18,520 --> 01:33:19,760
Hey-

1020
01:33:22,000 --> 01:33:23,331
You're alone, or...

1021
