1033
01:34:16,760 --> 01:34:19,843
<i>I'm better than you, you son of a bitch.</i>

1034
01:34:45,080 --> 01:34:48,402
<i>I always thought
I wanted to be exactly like my mom.</i>

1035
01:34:52,760 --> 01:34:55,366
<i>But she thinks she needs a man to be happy.</i>

1036
01:34:56,760 --> 01:34:58,091
<i>I don't.</i>

1037
01:35:03,480 --> 01:35:05,642
