1038
01:35:13,960 --> 01:35:16,327
<i>So, maybe nobody loves me.</i>

1039
01:35:17,120 --> 01:35:19,441
<i>Maybe nobody will ever love me.</i>

1040
01:35:21,120 --> 01:35:24,522
