being loved by somebody else.</i>

1041
01:35:50,400 --> 01:35:53,404
<i>This is for all the girls
when they have grown.</i>

1042
01:35:53,480 --> 01:35:56,609
<i>Signing off, trusty diary.</i>

1043
01:35:57,840 --> 01:36:01,162
<i>Love, Minnie Goetze.</i>